'''蘇格蘭FWA足球先生'''（'''Scottish Footballer of the Year'''，全名'''Scottish Football Writers' Association Footballer of the Year'''）是由「蘇格蘭足球記者協會」（Scottish Football Writers' Association，簡稱SFWA）的年度獎項，選出前一年的蘇格蘭年度最佳球員，被認為是蘇格蘭本土足球最重要的兩個個人獎項之一，另一個獎項為[[蘇格蘭PFA足球先生|蘇格蘭PFA足球先生]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.dailyrecord.co.uk/sport/football-news/scottish-football/spl-football/celtic-fc/2008/02/29/i-would-have-voted-for-ranger-alan-hutton-as-best-player-reveals-shunsuke-nakamura-86908-20335537/|title=I Would Have Voted For Ranger Alan Hutton As Best Player, Reveals Shunsuke Nakamura|work=Daily Record|location=Scotland|author=Neil Cameron|access-date=2008-02-29|date=2008-04-10|quote=We all have opinions about who is the season's best player and a year ago it was Nakamura who came out on top in voting for both the PFA and Football Writers' award.}}</ref>。該獎項自 1964-65年賽季開始頒發，最佳球員由蘇格蘭足球作家協會的成員投票選出，該協會由蘇格蘭各地的100多名足球記者組成<ref name="passion">{{cite web|url=http://www.sundayherald.com/sport/shfootball/display.var.1379865.0.fifty_years_of_passion_and_prose.php|title=Fifty years of passion and prose|author=Jim Black|work=Sunday Herald|access-date=2008-04-11}}{{dead link|date= 2017-10 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>。

